---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Contact — Easy Chat Maker"
  description="Get in touch with the Easy Chat Maker team for feedback, feature requests, bug reports or business enquiries."
  heading="Contact us"
>
  <p>
    We read everything — feedback, feature requests, bug reports, business enquiries and takedown
    requests. The fastest way to reach us:
  </p>

  <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
    <p class="!mt-0"><strong>Email</strong></p>
    <p class="!mt-1">
      <a href="mailto:hello@easychatmaker.com">hello@easychatmaker.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="!mt-3 text-[13.5px]">We usually reply within 1–2 business days.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Before you write</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Bug reports:</strong> include your browser, what you clicked, and a screenshot if
      possible — it helps us fix things fast.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Feature requests:</strong> tell us what you're trying to make; we prioritize by
      real use cases.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Content concerns:</strong> if you believe content made with this tool is being used
      to deceive or harm, contact us with details and we will respond promptly.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Common questions</h2>
  <p>
    The <a href="/#faq">FAQ on our homepage</a> answers the most frequent questions — pricing
    (it's free), supported platforms, group chats and export formats.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
